description: Database rules — Mongoose schemas, indexing, relationships, optimization
globs: server/src/models/**/*.ts

## Database Rules
1. Schemas match shared/types/ exactly
2. Embedded documents for one-to-few (stages → topics → resources)
3. References for one-to-many (user → paths)
4. Timestamps: true on all models
5. Index: userId on all user-scoped collections
6. Validate enums at schema level
7. .lean() for read-only queries
8. Limit results on high-volume collections (activity: 20)
9. Unique index on user email
